ingredientsDesc: Theophylline Sodium Glycinate is an equilibrium mixture containing Theophylline Sodium (C7H77N4NaO2) and Glycine (C2H5NO2) in approximately equimolecular proportions buffered with an additional mole of Glycine.Dried at 105℃ for 4 hours, it contains theophylline sodium glucinate equivalent to not less than 44.5% and not more than 47.3% anhydrous theophylline(C7H8N4O2).
